1. React form submits
2. Axios sends POST request
3. JWT goes in Authorization header
4. Middleware verifies token
5. req.userId is attached
6. Controller creates transaction
7. MongoDB stores document
8. JSON response returned
9. React refreshes transactions
10. Dashboard re-renders


React Form
    ↓
Axios
    ↓
Express Route
    ↓
Controller
    ↓
MongoDB



MongoDB
    ↓
Controller
    ↓
JSON Response
    ↓
React State
    ↓
UI